edu.cmu.sei.arche.vo
Class DesignRelationTypeVO

java.lang.Object
  edu.cmu.sei.arche.vo.DesignRelationTypeVO
public class DesignRelationTypeVO
extends java.lang.Object

Describes a design relation type, i.e., gives meta information that is associated with a generic design relation. Design relations are RF-independent and come from a separate XML configuration file. A design relation is necessarily a binary relation between two design elements, one is denominated the lhs and the other is the rhs element (for left- and right-hand side).

Author:
Neel Mullick
